s and similar technologies. This includes your IP address, browser type, device information, and pages you view. This helps us analyze site traffic, improve our websiteâ€™s functionality, and understand customer preferences.</p></li><li style="margin-top: 6px;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Dining Preferences:&nbsp;We may note dietary preferences or allergies you share with us to ensure your meal is prepared safely and to your liking.</p></li></ul><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin: 16px 0px;">How We Use Your Information</p><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin: 16px 0px;">Your information allows us to serve you better. Specifically, we use it to:</p><ul style="margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px;"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Process your reservations, online orders, and payments securely.</p></li><li style="margin-top: 6px;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Communicate with you about your orders, reservations, and any inquiries.</p></li><li style="margin-top: 6px;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Send you marketing communications, such as our newsletter featuring special offers and new menu items, but only if you have explicitly opted in. You can unsubscribe at any time.</p></li><li style="margin-top: 6px;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Improve our menu, services, and overall customer experience through aggregated, anonymous data analysis.</p></li><li style="margin-top: 6px;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Comply with legal obligations and protect against fraudulent activities.</p></li></ul><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin: 16px 0px;">Sharing Your Information</p><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin: 16px 0px;">We value your trust and do not sell your personal data to third parties. We only share your information in the following limited circumstances:</p><ul style="margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px;"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Service Providers:&nbsp;We work with trusted partners who assist us in operations, such as payment processors, delivery services, and marketing platforms. These partners are contractually bound to use your data only for the services we request and to protect its confidentiality.</p></li><li style="margin-top: 6px;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Legal Compliance:&nbsp;We may disclose information if required by law, such as in response to a court order or legal request.</p></li></ul><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin: 16px 0px;">Your Choices and Rights</p><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin: 16px 0px;">You have control over your personal information. You can:</p><ul style="margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px;"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Opt-out of marketing emails by using the "unsubscribe" link in every email.</p></li><li style="margin-top: 6px;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Disable cookies through your browser settings, though this may affect website functionality.</p></li><li style="margin-top: 6px;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Contact us to review, update, or delete the personal data we hold about you.</p></li></ul><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin: 16px 0px;">Data Security</p><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin: 16px 0px;">We implement robust security measures, including encryption and secure servers, to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction.</p><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin: 16px 0px;">Policy Updates</p><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style="margin: 16px 0px;">We may update this policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. The latest version will always be posted on our website with the effective date.</p></h3>',
